Note. This table shows published and unpublished detail for final sales of domestic computers and for
GDP less final sales of domestic computers. Series in this table have been used by BEA to estimate the
impact of changes in real final sales of domestic computers on changes in real GDP. Care should be taken
in interpreting these estimates because estimates for computers in change in inventories are not available
and because the computer components of some aggregates include parts (see table footnotes).
